                "description": "We study stand dynamics and how they can be influenced by man.  We thereby focus on the following topics:\r\n\r\n* Growth and yield research\r\n\r\n* Forest dynamics in forest reserves\r\n\r\n* Virgin forest research in the Ukraine\r\n\r\n* Adaptation of forest trees to climate change\r\n\r\n* Close-to-nature silvicultural strategies\r\n\r\n* Forest succession and young forest tending\r\n\r\n* Forest-ungulate interactions and browsing\r\n\r\nWe maintain and manage a net of long-term permanent plots and use the data in simulation models of forest dynamics. Our research contributes to an ecologically, economically and socially sustainable forest management.",
